    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Hunters Legend</strong> 是一款快节奏的 <strong>Looter-Shooter RPG</strong>，你将在激烈的战斗中收集强力武器、升级技能并击败敌人。<strong>单人游玩或与最多 4 名玩家合作</strong>，踏上找回失落记忆并推翻暴君 <strong>Duke Ducan</strong> 的冒险旅程！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激动人心的 Looter-Shooter RPG 冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/cfa385d57dc27cdce31c5547efd13e95.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/cfa385d57dc27cdce31c5547efd13e95.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Hunters Legend</strong> 将 <strong>快节奏射击、丰富武器库和深度角色自定义</strong> 相结合。击败敌人，收集稀有战利品，打造你的专属流派，成为对抗 <strong>Ducan 帝国</strong> 的无敌战士！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义你的猎人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/874c3ce32b78f8378f9caeafd8eb1483.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/874c3ce32b78f8378f9caeafd8eb1483.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/874c3ce32b78f8378f9caeafd8eb1483.mp4?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多个可玩角色中选择，每位角色都拥有独特的技能。每个猎人都有 <strong>3 个完整的技能树</strong>，你可以自由组合，再加上属性点分配、多种装备和武器槽位、丰富的词缀系统，以及决定流派的 <strong>Relic（遗物）</strong>——你需要发现、打造并升级它…… 这里的 <strong>RPG 深度远比看起来更丰富</strong>！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由选择游玩方式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/a5538741eeed36305622b7c44ec1f79f.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/a5538741eeed36305622b7c44ec1f79f.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/a5538741eeed36305622b7c44ec1f79f.mp4?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以 <strong>离线单人游玩</strong>，或与最多 <strong>三位好友在线合作</strong>。从一开始，你就可以专注于 <strong>30 小时的故事战役</strong>…… 或者完全跳过剧情，直接体验成长与终局玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁猎人的顺序完全由你决定，探索世界，挑战各种奖励和考验，尽情享受自由度极高的游戏体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入 <strong>Relic Hunters Legend 官方 Discord 频道（</strong>，抢先了解开发中的新内容，并直接与 <strong>Rogue Snail</strong> 团队交流——我们 <strong>始终倾听玩家的声音</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快节奏战斗，海量战利品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/67e40a8cdfd06aba8d1391e0106a0537.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/67e40a8cdfd06aba8d1391e0106a0537.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/67e40a8cdfd06aba8d1391e0106a0537.mp4?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有活动均支持单人游玩，并可 <strong>自动适应最多 4 人合作</strong>，包括：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小型开放世界探索区</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 种不同游戏模式的快节奏任务</strong>（交战、挖掘、运载、防御、干扰、裂隙、突袭）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带有随机修正的限时特殊任务</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拥有多个 Boss 的 Delve 地城</strong>（每个 Boss 都有独特的掉落表）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终局玩法</strong>：藏宝图、<strong>小行星地城 Boss</strong>、挑战模式等</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战利品不止于此！你还可以与不同派系建立友谊，完成声望任务，并通过 <strong>NPC 制作专属于你的完美装备或武器</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的装备 <strong>不是单纯的“装备评分堆叠”</strong>，游戏提供多种 <strong>高端稀有装备</strong>（<strong>异域、强化、套装、传奇和独特装备</strong>），加上 <strong>深度词缀系统</strong>，彻底改变你的游玩方式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入 <strong>Relic Hunters</strong>，在这场 <strong>充满动作的银河冒险</strong> 中证明你的实力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/fe3ebc6bba8e05efa9ec7136721e3743.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/fe3ebc6bba8e05efa9ec7136721e3743.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/fe3ebc6bba8e05efa9ec7136721e3743.mp4?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邪恶的帝国统治者 <strong>Duke Ducan</strong> 盗取了整个过去，并向所有人谎称自己是 <strong>一切美好事物的缔造者</strong>，借此巩固他 <strong>残暴的银河统治</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Hunters</strong> 由 <strong>Pinkyy</strong> 率领，他们穿梭于星系各地，寻找古代遗迹和文明遗物，希望恢复 <strong>真实的历史记忆</strong>。在旅途中，团队遇到了一位神秘的盟友——<strong>Seven</strong>，他 <strong>失去了所有记忆</strong>，却拥有能够 <strong>穿梭时间</strong> 的奇异能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想了解更多？我们的故事还在 <strong>漫画</strong>（讲述《Legend》之前的事件）和 <strong>动画短片</strong> 中扩展！快来 <strong>免费观看第 1、2、3 集</strong>，链接可在我们的 Steam 社区页面找到！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PC 优化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/e3f4ecbeee4f001c81c5905a04cd2417.poster.avif?t=1755196862\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/e3f4ecbeee4f001c81c5905a04cd2417.webm?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/633080/extras/e3f4ecbeee4f001c81c5905a04cd2417.mp4?t=1755196862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们对 <strong>Relic Hunters Legend</strong> 进行了精细优化，保证它像 <strong>经过精准调校的能量手枪</strong> 一样流畅运行！支持 <strong>4K 分辨率、无限制帧率、超宽屏</strong> 以及 <strong>完全自定义控制</strong>。不论你想要极致流畅的操作体验，还是最大化画面表现，我们都能满足你的需求！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于开发团队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你好！我们是 <strong>Rogue Snail</strong>，一家来自巴西的 <strong>独立、完全远程</strong> 游戏工作室。我们的使命？<strong>制作充满爱与热情的游戏</strong>！我们相信，<strong>当开发团队热爱自己的创作，这份热情也会渗透到最终的游戏体验中</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一款 Relic Hunters 游戏</strong> 都以 <strong>纯粹的乐趣和玩家社区</strong> 为核心。<strong>没有剥削性的机制，没有恶意的微交易，没有人为的阻碍</strong>，只有 <strong>最有趣的游戏体验</strong>，并且我们一直 <strong>与社区共同创造</strong>！</p>",
